		"description": "<p>In a fight, you exhibit a level of skilled brutality that few will ever witness and fewer can withstand. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>While you are raging, your jump distances triple.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency with the Athletics skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient.</li>\n<li>You learn an additional Tooth &amp; Claw maneuver of a level you could learn. It does not count against your maneuvers known.</li>\n<li>Half your berserker levels count as adept levels for the purpose of determining which Focus Feature options you can select.</li>\n</ul>",
